{"tid":445504,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"成語「鳴人不做暗事」出自火影邊一話?","createTime":"2017-10-23T12:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T13:33:13.000Z","uid":106675,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"29c3055c4c6660af83d541704e927f99d5c28bf4","tid":445504,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae91abd696379c93f13fdcfdd8780013958ad9f","tid":445504,"uid":36029,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"《富比世》（Forbes）雜誌歸納出5點運用幽默感的正確技巧：<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（１）別忘記自己的身分，如果身為主管，領導或管理才是你最重要的工作任務，而不是扮演一個喜劇演員。<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（２）作為朋友，彼此開玩笑吐槽或許無傷大雅；但主管跟員工開玩笑吐槽可就一點也不幽默，除非彼此之間長時間的工作情誼或穩固的信任感。<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（３）開自己玩笑不一定是幽默的表現，很可能因此傷人而不自知。特別是領導者，你的發言代表的並非個人，而是團隊，因此當你開自己玩笑時，很可能傷害了團隊。<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">（４）如果自己個性實在不適合，就別勉強自己耍幽默，以免弄巧成拙，氣氛冷場。</span></span><br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（５）幽默感也要看對象，你的玩笑幽默與否決定權在對方，而不在於你。如果對方不覺得幽默，那麼你的一番好意倒成了惡意。"},{"pid":"e1e936e9a403c3ada53e2f3d72aacfa6ebb95c11","tid":445504,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:42:27.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"4417aacfd7faa176ad9f39d350a7f6ba879d0215","tid":445504,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"成語出處：元 吳昌齡《張天師》第三折：&ldquo;常言道：&lsquo;明人不做那暗事&rsquo;，則俺這閉月羞花絕代姿，到如今自做出自當之，妝甚的謊子！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9935497222c3340154d40322f00c06185cdca7e9","tid":445504,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放桐生一馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"739063530a8b0b3887e9065ff65888df131bf7be","tid":445504,"uid":82404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b6436d9e35bc0615357abfd43d84c4f62fc7de","tid":445504,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"hahahahahha"},{"pid":"940566bb39abe09ac991ce71092aa639c523269c","tid":445504,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放桐生一馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></span></blockquote><br />\n反而呢個我笑左一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4d7c21fc03f132532d86aba15deeac0face396","tid":445504,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"呢個高質好多<br />\n<br />\n(IQ題..三頁開估)亞瑟王最想留住既人係邊個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/356568/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/356568/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8c14857bef52e2fcf6d8e15088a38af69d190ff","tid":445504,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac547f58c6d0a24c0d845c230c3ed954defdb71","tid":445504,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"說到做到就是我的忍道！"},{"pid":"e8cc9a869ed49875d3a1c13cc3c69957bd3e1014","tid":445504,"uid":152047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8605e66ef398620aa4cc27f12cfa7a8d23784c3f","tid":445504,"uid":33651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個高質好多<br />\n<br />\n(IQ題..三頁開估)亞瑟王最想留住既人係邊個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/356568/pag